                        <ns0:objectDesc>
                            <ns0:supportDesc>
                                <ns0:support><ns0:p>A large slab of cream/blue-grey marble, of which four joining fragments survive. Height (maximum across the face) 43.5 cm; width 52.2 cm; depth 4.5 cm (left) to 6 cm (right). Parts of the top, left and right margins survive, including the upper right corner. The upper left corner and all of the lower part of the slab are lost.</ns0:p>
